{"id":3519,"date":"2024-05-13T09:15:24","date_gmt":"2024-05-13T02:15:24","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/?p=3519"},"modified":"2024-05-13T09:15:29","modified_gmt":"2024-05-13T02:15:29","slug":"runner-giai-an-giang-dau-chan-huyen-bi-trai-nghiem-du-lich-nui-sam","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/runner-giai-an-giang-dau-chan-huyen-bi-trai-nghiem-du-lich-nui-sam\/","title":{"rendered":"Runner gi\u1ea3i &#8216;An Giang &#8211; D\u1ea5u ch\u00e2n huy\u1ec1n b\u00ed&#8217; tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m du l\u1ecbch n\u00fai Sam"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Runner \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i c\u00e1p treo mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed, h\u00f2a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng gian Ph\u1eadt gi\u00e1o thanh b\u00ecnh v\u00e0 chi\u00eam b\u00e1i Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u, Ch\u00f9a T\u00e2y An, Ch\u00f9a Hang.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y online An Giang &#8211; D\u1ea5u ch\u00e2n huy\u1ec1n b\u00ed di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 25\/3 \u0111\u1ebfn 28\/4, do khu du l\u1ecbch v\u0103n h\u00f3a t\u00e2m linh B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 &#8211; C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi FPT Online t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c. S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n thu h\u00fat h\u01a1n 5.000 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd tham gia tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 thao tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn vRace. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 runner \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BTC t\u1eb7ng v\u00e9 \u0111i c\u00e1p treo mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ebfn khu du l\u1ecbch N\u00fai Sam (Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, An Giang).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ban qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd khu du l\u1ecbch cho bi\u1ebft, sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m l\u01b0\u1ee3t runner c\u00f9ng gia \u0111\u1ebfn tham quan, tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5. D\u1ecbp ngh\u1ec9 l\u1ec5 30\/4 v\u1eeba qua, runner Nguy\u1ec5n Ng\u1ecdc Long c\u00f9ng nh\u00f3m b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i t\u1eeb TP HCM \u0111\u1ebfn An Giang, th\u0103m c\u00e1c danh th\u1eafng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng tr\u00ean n\u00fai Sam. &#8220;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean l\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh t\u1eeb c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng, khi BTC v\u1eeba m\u1edf gi\u1ea3i. C\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 cho du kh\u00e1ch kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, kh\u00f4ng gian m\u00e1t m\u1ebb, y\u00ean b\u00ecnh, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u01b0 th\u00e1i&#8221;, anh Long chia s\u1ebb.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"680\" height=\"528\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-26.jpeg\" alt=\"Ng\u1ecdc Long (ngo\u00e0i c\u00f9ng b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i) c\u00f9ng nh\u00f3m b\u1ea1n check in t\u1ea1i khu du l\u1ecbch N\u00fai Sam. \u1ea2nh: NVCC\" class=\"wp-image-3522\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-26.jpeg 680w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-26-600x466.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Ng\u1ecdc Long (ngo\u00e0i c\u00f9ng b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i) c\u00f9ng nh\u00f3m b\u1ea1n check in t\u1ea1i khu du l\u1ecbch N\u00fai Sam. \u1ea2nh:\u00a0NVCC<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p>Theo runner Ng\u1ecdc Long \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn anh \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 c\u00f4ng khai, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u00eam y\u1ebft, kh\u00f4ng t\u0103ng v\u00e0o c\u00e1c d\u1ecbp l\u1ec5, T\u1ebft. T\u1eeb khu v\u1ef1c b\u00e1n v\u00e9, du kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xe \u0111i\u1ec7n trung chuy\u1ec3n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eb1ng nh\u00e0 ga c\u00e1p treo.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i 900m, g\u1ed3m 37 cabin, m\u1ed7i cabin c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9a 8 h\u00e0nh kh\u00e1ch v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u l\u1ec5 c\u1ee7a du kh\u00e1ch th\u1eadp ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. &#8220;Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i \u0111i v\u00e0o d\u1ecbp l\u1ec5 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea3nh chen l\u1ea5n x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ea9y. C\u00e1c lu\u1ed3ng di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ban qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ph\u00e2n b\u1ed1 kh\u00e1 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00ean c\u00f3 \u1edf nh\u1eefng khu du l\u1ecbch t\u00e2m linh&#8221;, anh n\u00f3i.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"680\" height=\"383\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-27.jpeg\" alt=\"L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u tr\u00ean n\u00fai Sam. \u1ea2nh: Khu du l\u1ecbch n\u00fai Sam\" class=\"wp-image-3523\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-27.jpeg 680w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-27-600x338.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u tr\u00ean n\u00fai Sam. \u1ea2nh:\u00a0Khu du l\u1ecbch n\u00fai Sam<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p>Khu du l\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia n\u00fai Sam \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m du l\u1ecbch t\u00e2m linh n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u1edf Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, An Giang. N\u00fai Sam cao 284m, quy t\u1ee5 nhi\u1ec1u danh th\u1eafng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa x\u1ee9 N\u00fai Sam, L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u, Ch\u00f9a T\u00e2y An, Ch\u00f9a Hang, \u0111\u1ec1n Quan \u00c2m, \u0111\u1ec1n Ph\u1eadt Ng\u1ecdc&#8230; D\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i, du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt Th\u00edch Ca M\u00e2u Ni \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1, tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u01b0\u1ee1i m\u00e2y ng\u1eafm to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eafm m\u00ecnh trong kh\u00f4ng gian Ph\u1eadt gi\u00e1o thanh b\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh mang \u0111\u1eadm s\u1eafc m\u00e0u t\u00f4n gi\u00e1o, gia \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1edfi c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m check in nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u t\u00ecnh y\u00eau, tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m k\u00ednh vi\u1ec5n v\u1ecdng, tham gia l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i&#8230; Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn, c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh&#8221;, anh Ng\u1ecdc Long cho hay.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"680\" height=\"907\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-25.jpeg\" alt=\"Khu du l\u1ecbch t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ti\u1ebft m\u1ee5c ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 du kh\u00e1ch. \u1ea2nh: Khu du l\u1ecbch n\u00fai Sam\" class=\"wp-image-3521\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-25.jpeg 680w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-25-600x800.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Khu du l\u1ecbch t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ti\u1ebft m\u1ee5c ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 du kh\u00e1ch. \u1ea2nh:\u00a0<em>Khu du l\u1ecbch n\u00fai Sam<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p>Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a ban qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd khu du l\u1ecbch N\u00fai Sam, trong 5 ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 l\u1ec5, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00f3n 1.000 l\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00e1ch, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 160 l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 runner gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y An Giang \u2013 D\u1ea5u ch\u00e2n huy\u1ec1n b\u00ed. &#8220;Gi\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn r\u1ea5t m\u1edbi m\u1ebb, v\u1eeba mang \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u00fa v\u1ecb th\u00f4ng qua ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, v\u1eeba gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ebfn du kh\u00e1ch v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m du l\u1ecbch t\u00e2m linh n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00edch c\u1ea7u du l\u1ecbch, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kinh t\u1ebf&#8221;, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n BTC cho hay.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\n<p><strong>Ngu\u1ed3n th\u00f4ng tin<\/strong><\/p>\n<cite>B\u00e1o VnExpress | <a href=\"https:\/\/vnexpress.net\/runner-giai-an-giang-dau-chan-huyen-bi-trai-nghiem-du-lich-nui-sam-4744891.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/vnexpress.net\/runner-giai-an-giang-dau-chan-huyen-bi-trai-nghiem-du-lich-nui-sam-4744891.html<\/a><\/cite><\/blockquote>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Runner \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i c\u00e1p treo mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed, h\u00f2a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng gian Ph\u1eadt gi\u00e1o thanh b\u00ecnh v\u00e0 chi\u00eam b\u00e1i Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u, Ch\u00f9a T\u00e2y An, Ch\u00f9a Hang. Gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y online An Giang &#8211; D\u1ea5u ch\u00e2n huy\u1ec1n b\u00ed di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 25\/3 \u0111\u1ebfn 28\/4, do khu du l\u1ecbch v\u0103n h\u00f3a [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":3520,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[79,1],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3519"}],"co